msgstr "And a fitting answer to this would be: "

msgctxt "sn12.12:4.10"
msgid "‘phassapaccayā vedanā, vedanāpaccayā taṇhā’”ti. "
msgstr "‘Contact is a condition for feeling. Feeling is a condition for craving.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.14, sc5
#. VAR: tasatī”ti → taṇhīyatīti (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn12.12:5.1"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, bhante, tasatī”ti? "
msgstr "“But sir, who craves?” "

