msgid "“‘tasatī’ti ahaṃ na vadāmi. "
msgstr "“I don’t speak of one who craves. "

msgctxt "sn12.12:5.4"
msgid "‘Tasatī’ti cāhaṃ vadeyyaṃ, tatrassa kallo pañho: "
msgstr "If I were to speak of one who craves, then it would be fitting to ask "

msgctxt "sn12.12:5.5"
msgid "‘ko nu kho, bhante, tasatī’ti? "
msgstr "who craves. "

