msgstr "And a fitting answer to this would be: "

msgctxt "sn12.12:5.10"
msgid "‘vedanāpaccayā taṇhā, taṇhāpaccayā upādānan’”ti. "
msgstr "‘Feeling is a condition for craving. Craving is a condition for grasping.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn12.12:6.1"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, bhante, upādiyatī”ti? "
msgstr "“But sir, who grasps?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.12:6.2"
msgid "“No kallo pañho”ti bhagavā avoca: "
msgstr "“That’s not a fitting question,” said the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.12:6.3"
msgid "“‘upādiyatī’ti ahaṃ na vadāmi. "
msgstr "“I don’t speak of one who grasps. "

msgctxt "sn12.12:6.4"
msgid "‘Upādiyatī’ti cāhaṃ vadeyyaṃ, tatrassa kallo pañho: "
msgstr "If I were to speak of one who grasps, then it would be fitting to ask "

msgctxt "sn12.12:6.5"
msgid "‘ko nu kho, bhante, upādiyatī’ti? "
